What We Offer » Center City Settlement Services, LLC





















Menu











P: 215-988-9667 E: centercity@centercitysettlement.com












What We Offer

SERVICES AND BENEFITS
Personalized service, a single point of contact, fast turnaround time and a knowledgeable staff are among the many benefits of choosing Center City Settlement Services, for your settlement and escrow needs.
SPECIALIZING IN:
Title Insurance
Preparation of closing costs with lenders charges
Payoffs – ordering review through final payoff
Receipt, Review and Preparation of Closing Package
Title Searches
Coordinate Closing Date with all parties
Preparation of Post-Closing Packages
1031 exchanges to defer capital gains
Disbursement of Mortgage Funds
Notary Public















