Welcome to  Center City Settlement Services
Full-Service Title Insurance Agency
Center City Settlement Services, LLC is a full-service title insurance agency offering a complete range of title and escrow services for the public, the construction industry, attorneys, banks and other lenders, and the real estate industry. Center City Settlement Services is managed by Title Alliance, Ltd., and is a partnership between Title Alliance and Keller Williams Center City Philadelphia.
This partnership benefits the public and clients of Keller Williams Center City Philadelphia by providing title and escrow services on a flexible schedule, with the ability to provide closings throughout Pennsylvania.
Center City Settlement Services   is proud to have received a SOC I Attestation from Oread Partners, LLC combined with the SOC II Attestation received by Title Alliance! This puts Center City Settlement Services   in the forefront of customer security. These audits focused on financial controls, various company systems & procedures, and customer security. Center City Settlement Services   adheres to the ALTA Best Practices and monitors all policies to assure they remain in compliance.
Each of the licensed title, escrow, and/or settlement agents employed by Center City Settlement Services   is also vetted by Secured Settlements Inc. (SSI) SSI monitors thousands of title, settlement & and real estate legal firms, and nationwide through proprietary technology and the mortgage industry’s only National Settlement Agent Database. All employees have received a “low risk rating.”
Experience and expertise are fundamental to every service we provide, from application to closing. Rest assured you and your clients are in good hands.














